<form name="medical" action="/application/medical" method="post" class="form col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-4 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1">
  <h3 class="truncate-title">Would you like to apply for Medi-Cal?</h3>
  <div class="form-group">
    <div class="form-control subheader">
      <p>If you are eligible for Calfresh, you are also eligible for Medi-Cal. The Medi-Cal  program is a subsidized health insurance benefit. It covers services like doctor's visits, prescription drugs, and preventive care.</p>
      <p>If you do not currently have health insurance, it is recommended that you apply for this subsidized coverage.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="btn-group btn-group-justified" data-toggle="buttons">
      <button class="btn btn-primary form-button-2">
        <input type="radio" name="yes" id="yes" autofocus="autofocus"> Yes
      </button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary form-button-2">
        <input type="radio" name="no" id="no"> No
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="page-footer">
    <input class="btn next-step" type="submit" value="Next Step: Your Interview">
  </div>
</form>
<script>
  $('.btn').button()
</script>
